  "texts": [
    "As a model Hamiltonian, we consider a generalized Kondolattice Hamiltonian [32][33][34][35][36][37][38][39] as sketched in Fig. 1(a), incorporating the Kondo coupling between localized spins and the itinerant electrons, a direct coupling between the spin degrees of freedom, and disorder.",
    "On the one hand, we aim at establishing a comprehensive understanding of the relaxation dynamics depending on the model parameters and for idealized initial conditions in the spin sector.",
    "On the other hand, we want to address the issue of thermalization.Both the cases of a coupling of an optically excited electron to phonons and magnons have been investigated.",
    "For the former, we mention [22,[40][41][42], while for the latter, Refs.",
    "[24,43,44] are examples."
  ],
